01,Whale Rechargeable Water Table Pump with Sprinkler (Blue Purple),inputs/reference_images/01.webp,"Use the reference image as the source of truth for the product color, shape, and branding. Place the blue purple whale-shaped water pump with sprinkler attachment on a low shelf inside a bright, busy toy store — think Target toy aisle or a kids' outdoor section. Surrounding shelves slightly visible in soft focus background with colorful packaging. Lighting is natural overhead retail fluorescent, slightly warm. Shot feels like a casual iPhone photo taken mid-aisle by a parent browsing. No price tags visible. No blurred background. No studio lighting. No CGI sheen. Slight lens imperfection. Product is the clear focal point with nothing crowding it directly. True to size — looks like a handheld pump accessory, not oversized.","Slow handheld push toward the whale water pump sitting on the toy store shelf. Camera drifts in naturally, slightly unsteady like a real phone video. A single hand enters from the right, gently taps/pokes the top of the whale pump, then pulls back. Camera eases out to show the full product on the shelf. Product label and whale shape clearly visible within first 3 seconds. One hand only. No zoom cuts — continuous natural motion. 5 seconds total.",image_submitted,fe_id_cf8a7649-c4aa-4898-be00-98f32c26be6d,/fx/api/trpc/media.getMediaUrlRedirect?name=0108ee75-995e-4fc1-9c32-050da90ea455,f8964286-78c2-41d6-8413-075968880784,/fx/tools/flow/project/26ec047b-73c6-45c6-b201-f332fa786267/edit/61085cc5-99e7-479a-89fa-e25bbd378dc4,auto,,,,
02,Miracle Mold Remover Gel + Scrub Brush (7oz),inputs/reference_images/02.webp,"Use the reference image as the source of truth for the product — a 7oz gel tube/bottle of Miracle Mold Remover with a scrub brush included. Place both items together on a cleaning products shelf inside a pharmacy or home goods store — think CVS cleaning aisle or a Walmart household section. Shelf label strips slightly visible below, other cleaning products softly blurred in background. Overhead retail lighting, slightly cool/white. Photo looks like it was taken on an iPhone by someone casually browsing the cleaning aisle. No price tags. No studio gloss. Slight natural imperfection in the shot. Product is the clear focal point. Both the gel and brush are fully visible and true to size.","Slow handheld camera push toward the mold remover gel and scrub brush sitting side by side on the pharmacy shelf. Slight natural camera shake as it drifts in. A single hand enters from the left, picks up the gel bottle briefly to show the front label, sets it back down. Camera pulls back to reveal both products together on the shelf. Label text clearly readable within first 3 seconds. One hand only. Smooth continuous motion, no cuts. 5 seconds total.",image_submitted,fe_id_5b8130fc-434f-41f8-9f77-6d6062cfecc3,/fx/api/trpc/media.getMediaUrlRedirect?name=f4e1a459-bdcf-44f5-874d-b86595214676,6f774a04-d564-4a61-926e-6a7d5dd27a31,/fx/tools/flow/project/26ec047b-73c6-45c6-b201-f332fa786267/edit/fad7ae88-00ba-49af-aa72-973d276c46e6,auto,,,,
03,ANTA UNISEX KAI 1 Basketball Shoes (Black White),inputs/reference_images/03.webp,"Use the reference image as the source of truth for the shoe colorway — black and white ANTA KAI 1 basketball shoes. Place a single shoe (or pair angled naturally) on a low display shelf inside a sports or shoe store — think Foot Locker or a Dick's Sporting Goods footwear wall. Other sneakers softly visible on shelves in the background. Retail overhead lighting with slight warm tone. Shot looks like an iPhone photo taken by a shopper crouching down to check out the shoe. No price tags. No studio background. No CGI reflections. Slight natural grain. Shoe is the full focal point, nothing directly beside it competing for attention. True to size — reads as a full-size adult basketball shoe.","Slow handheld push toward the black and white ANTA KAI 1 sitting on the shoe store display shelf. Camera drifts in low and slightly angled, natural handheld wobble. A single hand enters from the right, taps the toe box of the shoe lightly, then withdraws. Camera eases back to show the full shoe and surrounding shelf context. ANTA branding and KAI 1 detail visible within first 3 seconds. One hand only. No jump cuts — fluid motion throughout. 5 seconds total.",image_submitted,fe_id_03b13548-473c-4843-9f55-290cece7ab61,/fx/api/trpc/media.getMediaUrlRedirect?name=c0325730-84d3-4c80-8e9c-3e16a59b3f17,c44e8398-d47d-4625-a296-662e4cfba67b,/fx/tools/flow/project/26ec047b-73c6-45c6-b201-f332fa786267/edit/369bb8fd-ec53-4f47-a8a9-96b937515398,auto,,,,
04,"ONBRILL 13/10FT Cantilever Patio Umbrella with Base (Adjustable Tilt, Double-Sided)",inputs/reference_images/04.webp,"Use the reference image as the source of truth for the umbrella — a large cantilever offset patio umbrella with visible base, adjustable tilt mechanism, and double-sided canopy. Place it on a display floor inside a large home goods or outdoor furniture store — think Home Depot garden center or a Costco seasonal outdoor section. Other patio furniture and umbrellas softly visible in the background. Bright overhead warehouse-style retail lighting. Shot looks like a casual iPhone photo taken by someone walking through the outdoor section. No price tags. No studio backdrop. No glossy CGI finish. Umbrella is fully open and upright, base visible at the bottom, the full canopy span readable. True to scale — looks impressively large. Slight natural photo imperfection.","Slow handheld walk toward the open cantilever umbrella standing on the home store floor display. Camera approaches from slightly below the canopy edge, drifting naturally with mild handheld shake. A single hand enters from the left and gently pushes one of the canopy ribs to show the tilt mechanism, then pulls back. Camera eases out to frame the entire umbrella including the base. Canopy color and offset arm clearly visible within first 3 seconds. One hand only. Continuous smooth motion, no cuts. 5 seconds total.",pending,,,,,auto,,,,
